<div class="hotspotminingContent_pic ">
<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/tashuo/browse/content?id=7a442b4090860fc8e0b3fbe1&lemmaId=1017726&lemmaId=1017726&fr=qingtian" target="_blank"><img src="https://gss0.bdstatic.com/94o3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/whfpf%3D360%2C280%2C50/sign=815a38b837dbb6fd250eb6666f19982e/95eef01f3a292df5307e2056b2315c6034a87330.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class="hotspotminingContent_cnt ">
<div class="hotspotminingContent_cnt_tit"><span class="hotspotminingContent_cnt_tit_tit"><a href="https://baike.baidu.com/tashuo/browse/content?id=7a442b4090860fc8e0b3fbe1&lemmaId=1017726&lemmaId=1017726&fr=qingtian" target="_blank">读贾岛：诗词不止于“推”或“敲”,“推敲”的背后是多彩的人生</a></span><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/configModule/hotspotmining/img/flag_new_5f5180c.png" />
<span class="hotspotminingContent_cnt_tit_tim">2019-05-01 12:05</span>
</div>
<div class="hotspotminingContent_cnt_cnt">
<span>贾岛“推敲”犹豫不绝，可见性格是典型的文人性格，遇事不好决断，谨小慎微。韩愈当时已是高官，志得意满，无形之中也把性格带入诗词，“敲”字背后，可见满满的官威。</span><a href="https://baike.baidu.com/tashuo/browse/content?id=7a442b4090860fc8e0b3fbe1&lemmaId=1017726&lemmaId=1017726&fr=qingtian" target="_blank">...详情</a></div>
</div>
