<div class="hotspotminingContent_cnt ">
<div class="hotspotminingContent_cnt_tit"><span class="hotspotminingContent_cnt_tit_tit"><a href="https://baike.baidu.com/tashuo/browse/content?id=2e7f4fcdd7ef6a101416ef31&fr=qingtian&lemmaId=1017726" target="_blank">唐朝“苦吟派”诗人贾岛是苦吟还是苦逼？</a></span><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/configModule/hotspotmining/img/flag_new_5f5180c.png" />
<span class="hotspotminingContent_cnt_tit_tim">2018-04-06 02:04</span>
</div>
<div class="hotspotminingContent_cnt_cnt">
<span>岛就是因吟《病蝉》诗，被认为是语含讥刺，权贵们眦牙必报，说岛在考场内举止疯狂，破坏了科考秩序，将岛列入“十恶”，驱逐出京。从此，贾岛告别长安，告别科考，一生与功名无缘。</span><a href="https://baike.baidu.com/tashuo/browse/content?id=2e7f4fcdd7ef6a101416ef31&fr=qingtian&lemmaId=1017726" target="_blank">...详情</a></div>
