<ul class="tashuo-list">
<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoId="2e7f4fcdd7ef6a101416ef31">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=1efbdf04&authorId=222bebc5db0a5b24b0bd5e21&from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/6609c93d70cf3bc756fb14c4da00baa1cd112a1b.jpg" /></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>写乎</strong>
<span>探究历史悬疑，挖掘地方风物</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=2e7f4fcdd7ef6a101416ef31&lemmaId=1017726&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" class="cover" target="_blank">
<img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/d62a6059252dd42a7088dad50f3b5bb5c8eab8cf.jpg" data-width="" data-height="" class="cover-img">
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"></div>
<p class="title">
唐朝“苦吟派”诗人贾岛是苦吟还是苦逼？
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=2e7f4fcdd7ef6a101416ef31&lemmaId=1017726&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
岛就是因吟《病蝉》诗，被认为是语含讥刺，权贵们眦牙必报，说岛在考场内举止疯狂，破坏了科考秩序，将岛列入“十恶”，驱逐出京。从此，贾岛告别长安，告别科考，一生与功名无缘。</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2018-04-05</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">236</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoId="35fbbd535ca2950ada7ea302">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=0fe67ca0&authorId=f97c8e26447fa302f5c2c220&from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/64380cd7912397ddffbeacc15582b2b7d1a2872b.jpg" /></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>历史客栈</strong>
<span>有趣味、有思维、有品位的“三味”历史</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=35fbbd535ca2950ada7ea302&lemmaId=1017726&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" class="cover" target="_blank">
<img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/472309f7905298221b23c755ddca7bcb0a46d410.jpg" data-width="" data-height="" class="cover-img">
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"></div>
<p class="title">
真实的贾岛撞车事件，远比你知道的要残酷得多
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=35fbbd535ca2950ada7ea302&lemmaId=1017726&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
贾岛的第一个故事版本能一直流传下来也就不难理解了，不光是文人在推崇，老百姓们也都很认可，因为它让人感受到了这个世界的温暖。至于故事的真和假，倒没那么重要了。</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2017-07-14</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">221</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoId="9a720ebdbf9939c5236a5ad2">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=eae35e14&authorId=f484cb0e5420b0bd57ab5d21&from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/b21bb051f8198618877f954646ed2e738bd4e63c.jpg" /></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>少读红楼</strong>
<span>文化自媒体，书评人</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=9a720ebdbf9939c5236a5ad2&lemmaId=1017726&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" class="cover" target="_blank">
<img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/472309f790529822452af53cd9ca7bcb0a46d430.jpg" data-width="" data-height="" class="cover-img">
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"></div>
<p class="title">
二流诗人却拥有一级流量：贾岛和他的狂热粉丝们
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=9a720ebdbf9939c5236a5ad2&lemmaId=1017726&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
对于这些诗人们来说，贾岛的意义估计远要大于李白、杜甫，虽然贾岛在唐代诗坛中默默无闻，但是在后世却有着独特的地位。</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2019-06-26</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">161</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoId="6985b0e6f45ff0b9c441d043">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=1efbdf04&authorId=222bebc5db0a5b24b0bd5e21&from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/6609c93d70cf3bc756fb14c4da00baa1cd112a1b.jpg" /></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>写乎</strong>
<span>探究历史悬疑，挖掘地方风物</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=6985b0e6f45ff0b9c441d043&lemmaId=1017726&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" class="cover" target="_blank">
<img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/b03533fa828ba61ec6fcca164d34970a304e59fc.jpg" data-width="" data-height="" class="cover-img">
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"></div>
<p class="title">
偶像就是这么屌：大唐毒舌诗人贾岛，敢说皇上不懂诗
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=6985b0e6f45ff0b9c441d043&lemmaId=1017726&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
很难想象，如果没有贾岛这一抹异样的色彩，大唐的诗空是否会暗淡一些，但至少会失去一些多样性。贾岛正是凭借对诗歌艺术殚精竭虑的单纯性领悟了最深的生命感受，进而超越了皇权，超越了正统，超越了人与人之间的尊卑地位，而抵达了一种生命的平等，并用他的行为艺术，把自己活成了一个诗篇。</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2018-02-13</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">143</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li class="slider-item">
<ul class="tashuo-list">
<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoId="d49633ff2278b896d1354ebc">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=1efbdf04&authorId=222bebc5db0a5b24b0bd5e21&from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/6609c93d70cf3bc756fb14c4da00baa1cd112a1b.jpg" /></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>写乎</strong>
<span>探究历史悬疑，挖掘地方风物</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=d49633ff2278b896d1354ebc&lemmaId=1017726&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" class="cover" target="_blank">
<img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/3bf33a87e950352a9b24e4d15d43fbf2b3118ba6.jpg" data-width="" data-height="" class="cover-img">
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"></div>
<p class="title">
孟郊与贾岛这两位仁兄堪称中国诗歌史上最苦逼最悲催的存在？
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=d49633ff2278b896d1354ebc&lemmaId=1017726&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
孟郊与贾岛的身后事都是朋友帮忙料理的，所谓一贫如洗，正是如此。韩愈诗云，“孟郊死葬北邙山，从此风云得暂闲。天恐文章浑断绝，故生贾岛著人间”，诗囚诗奴，天生耳。人总要留下些什么，不然不是白白来了这人世一遭。</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2019-08-11</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">133</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul></div>
